                           <q xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc"><hi rend="italic">Kissahi Char Derwish</hi></q> (Tale of the Four Dervishes).
                        </item>
                     </list>
                        <label>Bookplates:</label>
                        <list>
                        <item>
                           <locus from="Inner_back_cover" to="Inner_back_cover">Left paste-down,</locus> <q xml:lang="en">Bibliotheca Lindesiana</q> with shelfmark <q>F/9</q>, and <q>Bland MSS No. 424</q>.
                        </item>
